           MOVE    PTCOM-REC           TO  MCPDATA-REC
           MOVE    "DBSELECT"          TO  MCP-FUNC
           MOVE    "PTCOM-KEY"         TO  ORC-DBPATH
           CALL    "ORCMCPSUB"          USING
